wiki.summary: “fukumean” is a high-energy track where Gunna taps into the melodies that initially established him into the modern rap scene. On it, Gunna bounces back from a dark period of his life in good spirits, shown by confident, braggadocios lyrics. As of 2023, it is Gunna’s best performing song on the Billboard Hot 100 following “pushin P” which peaked at #7 on January 22, 2022. On it, Gunna bounces back from a dark period of his life in good spirits, shown by confident, braggadocios lyrics.
